snippet.title: Ho-Ho-Home Invasion - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
In a game we definitely didn't consider calling "Santa Game Solid", help Santa complete his Santa training ahead of the Christmas period by delivering presents without getting caught!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1482830/HoHoHome_Invasion
Itch: https://whitepotstudios.itch.io/hohohomeinvasion
In-game music included in trailer generated by Evoke AI (https://evokemusic.ai)
